annotationA: CG2918, isoform A; It is involved in the biological process described with: multicellular organism reproduction; protein folding; Belongs to the heat shock protein 70 family
annotationB: Calreticulin; Molecular calcium-binding chaperone promoting folding, oligomeric assembly and quality control in the ER via the calreticulin/calnexin cycle.
